Once the design details are complete, the permitting and agency correspondence will be initiated.
Abandonment in place is proposed for the outfall pipe and manholes along Otter Creek and within Otter Cove.
Any structures or parts of structures above existing grade will be removed to grade and any depressions created will be filled.
