Summary of Agency and Public Consultation A.
Public Participation Efforts: A number of public information meetings including formal presentations, Selectman meetings, and two public votes were conducted in order to include public participation in the planning process.
Both votes were in favor of the consolidation of the Otter Creek and Seal Harbor facilities.
